<ab facs="#facs_16_r1l21">elıche vvirtin <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> / vvie daʒ ſıe etwas ſache bey ew cʒehandeln </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_16_r1l22"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darümb ſie den Markart waltman <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_16_r1l23"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> weiſheit ſchicken / euch die von Jren wegen cʒuercʒelen / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_16_r1l24">vvaʒ der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıener ~ darümb von der <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Burgers </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_16_r1l25">vnd ~ <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> wirtin wegen an euch bring vnd werb / daʒ Jr Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_16_r1l26">darynne durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen <expan>fürderlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd beholffen ſein wöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_16_r1l27">Als etc das wöllen etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>a</ex>to</expan> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> / <expan>b<ex>ea</ex>to<ex>rum</ex></expan> Petri et Pauli <expan>Ap<ex>oſto</ex>lo<ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab>
